.DT
is_number_type
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
is_number_type

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_number_type -  This checks to make sure that the type is a number based type.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_number_type(int type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type to check
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if it is a number, 0 if not

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/expressions.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This checks to make sure that the type is a number based type.
This can be controlled to make sure that any added types are also
allowed to be treated as numbers.
.EP

